config BR2_PACKAGE_JACK_EXAMPLE_TOOLS
	bool "jack-example-tools"
	depends on BR2_PACKAGE_JACK2
	help
	  JACK example / CLI tools, split out of jack2 upstream into their
	  own project. Provides jack_lsp, jack_connect, jack_disconnect,
	  jack_transport, jack_samplerate, jack_bufsize, jack_wait,
	  jack_metro, jack_load, jack_unload, jack_property, jack_evmon,
	  jack_midi_dump and friends.

	  Builds against jack2's jack.pc; at runtime they connect to
	  whatever JACK server owns the socket (on PanicOS that is PipeWire
	  via the libjack compat shim).

	  https://github.com/jackaudio/jack-example-tools
